            <title>[HBASE-2996] Fix and clean up Maven</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-2996</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I have some changes to the pom.xml that are already covered by a few other issues which I&apos;d like to do in one big patch (because that&apos;s the way I started it). I can always split that up in smaller parts if needed.&lt;/p&gt;

